								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 1.332-7.257 3 3 0 0 0-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 0 0-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 0 0 2.25 15Z" />
							</svg>
							<h3>Cloud Migration</h3>
							<p>Data center analysis and sizing, cost projections, tech selection (e.g. serverless, SaaS, PaaS) and implementation. BC/DR design and IaC.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="service-card">
							<svg class="service-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
