							<h3>Data Engineering</h3>
							<p>EAI, ODS and data lake design and build-out. Telemetry and mass-scale, event-driven processing.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="service-card">
							<svg class="service-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
